'Learn the importance of the value of perseverance as you follow the footsteps of Sir Edmund Hillary up Mt Everest.
'Progressing through this game requires knowledge and logical thought as you complete riddles and learn about Sir Edmund Hillary's life.
'This application is perfect for all ages with its easy to use User Interface, which allows users to make the most of the application.
'The comprehensive settings menu allows the user to personalize their experience, enhancing game play.
'The multi-choice option allows the user to make the questions easier should they struggle with the more complicated questions. 
'The high quality animations allow for a smooth game play experience
'/////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
'Students often fail to understand the relevance of the RAPID values system.
'This is an important issue that the brand new game "Riddle Mountain" endeavours to solve. 
'It follows the life of Sir Edmund Hillary, showing students how the system can be implemented in everyday life.

'This application combines high quality graphics, challenging scenarios and interactive game-play,
'both to teach the user about these important values and to create a game-play experience that tests your logical thinking and general knowledge.
'It's uncompromising attention to detail provides all users with a pleasant experience, with smooth animations, 
'an easy-to-use Interface and a comprehensive settings menu for a enjoyable, personalized experience. 
'This application combines advanced design philosophies and high end programming to provide the most amazing user experience possible. 
'The game includes a useful multi-choice function for the more complicated questions making the game perfect for all ages and abilities. 
'This application is the perfect way to teach students the value of the RAPID system in a fun, engaging way, far exceeding any of its competitors.
'/////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

